'''Spain''' is an original [[Nations|country]] that was on BitLife in September 2018. Its default cities are the capital, Madrid, along with A Coruña, Barcelona, Bilbao,  Granada, Malaga, Palma,  Pamplona, Pontevedra, Rota, San Sebastian, Seville, Valencia, Valladolid, and Zaragoza.
